{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was early spring, which is pretty cold, and I was still wearing a coat and the day's are not very long, so it was dusk outside.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So called some-- some party official.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put me in-- in a-- in a private car-- it was not the police or anything-- and took me to the police [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] holding place-- which had 100 years ago, or till the end of the monarchy, been the barracks for the regiment, for the Vienna regiment.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] barracks, large barracks, [SPEAKING GERMAN] on the Donaukanal-- red brick, big towers, very impressive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was taken there and this person who brought me, because they didn't know what to do with me, just put me down there at the-- at the entrance, at the officer's desk and took off and didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously, there was no file.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knew whom they had or why they had her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took my belt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was wearing a suit with a belt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took my hat and my gloves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they left everything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nothing was said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing was explained, or-- nothing nice or ugly happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then somebody opened a cell door and pushed me in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This happen to be a single cell, and there were four or five people in it already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since by then it was dark, and it was close to 7:00, they had had their evening meal, and they had gotten ready for the night.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, since it was a single cell, and it was so overcrowded, they slept on straw mattresses on the floor, which means that the entire floor was covered.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
